<function>

access:   public

name: exec

param: string, $stmt

param: array, $data, array ()

return: object

</function>

Prepares and executes an SQL statement with bound data.

* Parameters:

 * string //$stmt//: The text of the SQL statement, with placeholders.

 * array //$data//: An associative array of data to bind to the placeholders.

* Returns object: A PDOStatement object.

Prepares and executes an SQL statement with bound data.